{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779177889147,"sessionID":"ses_1c0bd0875ffeDBfk5LNf5rH20A","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"webfetch","callID":"call_01_bXEAOKJA7L8e7pygeJMM8022","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"timeout":30,"url":"https://adamfard.com/blog/rental-platform-ux","format":"markdown"},"output":"UI UX Design Agency for SaaS, Fintech & AI | Adam Fard UX Studio \n\n[](/)\n\n-   [Our Projects](/ux-projects)\n-   [Solutions](/#)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Create MVPFrom nothing to a research-backed no-code prototype: you'll be sure to impress investors.\n    \n    ](/ux-ui-design-services#mvp)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Improve ProductReached PMF? We help you to scale your product without scaling the problems.\n    \n    ](/ux-ui-design-services#scale)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Customer researchKnow your (potential) users better than they know themselves.\n    \n    ](/ux-ui-design-services#research)\n    \n    [\n    \n    DesignStream Subscription\n    \n    -   Unlimited UX / UI Tasks\n    -   Unlimited Revisions\n    -   2 Days Turnaround Time\n    -   Project Management\n    \n    ![](/static/ux-design-agency-4-f773052c59837895521f19104191f67b.jpg)\n    \n    ](/unlimited-ux-ui-design-subscription)\n    \n    [\n    \n    ⚡ Fast UX Design Review \\-40% Get a 60+ page review of your product to eliminate all UX issues & skyrocket conversion, activation and retention.\n    \n    ![](/static/ux-review-report-b4e2fc39a551aedd6130fd9020550e6b.png)\n    \n    \n    \n    ](/ai-ux-design-review)\n    \n-   [Industries](/#)\n    \n    [\n    \n    FintechMaking financial products crystal clear\n    \n    ](/fintech-design)\n    \n    [\n    \n    AIDefining the future of humanity & digital experience\n    \n    ](/ai-design-agency)\n    \n    [\n    \n    SaaSDesigning analytics, AI platforms, dashboards\n    \n    ](/saas-design)\n    \n    [\n    \n    EdtechMaking educational products fun and engaging\n    \n    ](/edtech-design)\n    \n-   [About Us](/#)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Our Story & Why Us\n    \n    ](/about-us)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Our UX Design Process\n    \n    ](/ux-design-process)\n    \n-   [UX Resources](/#)\n    \n    [\n    \n    AI + UX eBookMaximize Your AI Knowledge\n    \n    ](https://adamfard.com/ai-ux-ebook)\n    \n    [\n    \n    UX BlogArticles and Stories\n    \n    ](/blog)[\n    \n    See All DownloadsUX Templates, Checklists & Guides\n    \n    ](/download-ux-resources)\n    \n    [\n    \n    UX Pilot AIGenerate UX/UI Superfast!\n    \n    \n    \n    ](https://uxpilot.ai?source=adamfard.com)\n    \n\n-   UX Services\n    \n-   [Research & UX / UI Design](/ux-ui-design-services)\n-   [Unlimited Subscription](/unlimited-ux-ui-design-subscription)\n-   [Fast UX Review](/fast-ux-design-review)\n-   Case Studies\n    \n-   [Past Projects](/ux-projects)\n-   Industries\n    \n-   [AI](/ai-design-agency)\n-   [Fintech](/fintech-design)\n-   [SaaS](/saas-design)\n-   About Us\n    \n-   [Our Story & Why Us](/about-us)\n-   UX Resources\n    \n-   [UX Blog](/blog)\n-   [Downloads](/download-ux-resources)\n\nUX Design Agency & AI Dev Studio\n\n# Your UX & AI Studio for  \nB2B SaaS Products\n\n[See Services](#services)\n\nTrusted by companies like\n\n## Have you ever been down this road?\n\nOur UX & AI Agency can help\n\nProduct Challenges\n\nIcon For Road-Cone\n\nWhat other companies do\n\nIcon For Shovel\n\nWhat we do\n\n-   For most tech ventures, product performance is synonymous with business performance. However, despite the vitality of the product's success, the problems below couldn't be any more common.\n    \n    -   Low activation & adoption\n        \n    -   Low retention\n        \n    -   High churn\n        \n    \n-   These problems, being so common, call for decisive and drastic solutions. The solutions, below, however, only scratch the surface of the deep underlying problems.\n    \n    -   Increase the Marketing & Sales Budget\n        \n    -   Hire more people\n        \n    -   Launch new features\n        \n    -   Retarget customers\n        \n    \n-   Before pouring your budget into marketing, team composition, and sales, you should build a solid foundation with an outstanding product experience. That's what we do. We design products that market themselves to make your job that much easier.\n    \n    -   Boost perceived value\n        \n    -   Revamp the User Experience\n        \n    -   In-depth research to inform product design\n        \n    -   Foster our clients' UX maturity\n        \n    -   Validating all product ideas before going all in\n        \n    \n\nProduct challenges\n\nFor most tech ventures, product performance is synonymous with business performance. However, despite the vitality of the product's success, the problems below couldn't be any more common.\n\n-   Low activation & adoption\n    \n-   Low retention\n    \n-   High churn\n    \n\nWhat other companies do\n\nThese problems, being so common, call for decisive and drastic solutions. The solutions, below, however, only scratch the surface of the deep underlying problems.\n\n-   Increase the Marketing & Sales Budget\n    \n-   Hire more people\n    \n-   Launch new features\n    \n-   Retarget customers\n    \n\nWhat we do\n\nBefore pouring your budget into marketing, team composition, and sales, you should build a solid foundation with an outstanding product experience. That's what we do. We design products that market themselves to make your job that much easier.\n\n-   Boost perceived value\n    \n-   Revamp the User Experience\n    \n-   Conduct thorough user research to inform product design\n    \n-   Foster our clients' UX maturity\n    \n-   Validating all product ideas before going all in\n    \n\n## Here's how we've helped our clients\n\n[See all reviews](https://clutch.co/profile/adam-fard-ux-studio#reviews)\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg height='506' width='800' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' version='1.1'%3E%3C/svg%3E)\n\n![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)\n\n![](/static/895ab751aa8f3a4e9ca4cc876c007054/402c3/alm.jpg)\n\nRichard Caruso\n\nSenior VP of products at ALM\n\n![](data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg height='457' width='800' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' version='1.1'%3E%3C/svg%3E)\n\n![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)\n\n![](/static/ab7ff2edd278f7851ae8ec9d9cbc6520/139d0/wevett.jpg)\n\nShannon Kaufman\n\nCo-Founder of WeVett\n\nAdam Fard AI Studio gave us the hands-on feeling of a small shop and the quality and professionalism of a big shop.\n\n![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)\n\n![](/static/9e7833718e9e041913edc4ba4dae5819/e404e/agent-avatar.jpg)\n\nThe team delivered an excellent UX design that was also technically sound and ready for development. They efficiently translated our requirements into both user-friendly designs and clean, implementable code.\n\n![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)\n\n![](/static/e03811068690e8e469f23e7fb4e02fbc/e404e/think-avatar.jpg)\n\nThe MVP exceeded expectations with its seamless user experience and robust technical implementation. Adam Fard AI studio delivered an intuitive interface optimized for conversion, backed by clean, maintainable code that scales. Their expertise in both UX design and development resulted in a product that delights users while meeting all technical requirements.\n\n![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)\n\n![](/static/2c0ce144389fdaff1486b7e5a3209173/e404e/qolo-avatar.jpg)\n\n## We've done this many times\n\nFEATURED UX CASE STUDIES\n\n![](data:image/png;base64,)\n\n![Thinkpricing](/static/786cf21775605d6e4a2415fa62bc7d03/cf08a/home-projects-thinkpricing.png)\n\n##### th!nkpricing\n\n## AI Sales intelligence tool\n\nThe th!nkpricing app is a SaaS solution that boosts revenue by optimizing the service or product price based on demand and supply. The app is backed by data science and AI which is perfect for Sports, Cinema, Entertainment, and Ski Resorts.\n\n-   **Increased users' trust, in the platform's AI;**\n-   **Able to retain current users**, which resulted in an increase of the marketing budget to acquire new customers and confidently scale;\n-   **Clear product design process and team facilitation;**\n\n[AI platform case study](https://adamfard.com/projects/saas-b2b-platform)\n\n##### Marginal Unit\n\n## Power Market Analytics\n\nMarginal Unit develops and operates innovative analytics solutions for the power market analytics. the mission is to help power traders and asset managers elevate their business to new heights by making traditionally complex power market analysis quicker, simpler, and more accurate.\n\n-   **Improved the information architecture** of the product;\n-   Improved discoverability of features and onboarding of new users, **increasing activation and retention rates;**\n-   Consolidated and developed a **scalable design system** to accelerate the design and development process.\n\n![](data:image/png;base64,)\n\n![MU - Power Market Analytics](/static/3feb58a74867b15a67dadedaf45c8101/7f7d9/home-projects-marginal.png)\n\n![](data:image/png;base64,)\n\n![Qolo](/static/39c040b5c01dc5d1f9e524030e1c6338/d4ca8/home-projects-sciforma.png)\n\n##### Sciforma + One2Team\n\n## Merged 2 ERP’s into 1\n\nSciforma is an enterprise Project and Portfolio Management software. In 2021 they acquired One2Team and merged both platforms.\n\n-   192 user research findings and 100+ design recommendations;\n-   279 designed screens and 90% of usability issues uncovered;\n-   **Increased Customer Satisfaction score from 3 to 8.**\n\n##### Kinteract\n\n## Multiplatform Learning Management System\n\nAn Edtech platform for facilitating communication among students, parents, and teachers.\n\n-   **78% of Increase in the conversion rate** Thanks to better usability, the schools are a lot more likely to upgrade their trial accounts and become paying customers.\n-   **Acquisition of new clients** Based on new tailored features and interactive prototypes we helped acquire big clients: UK Government, Sharjah Ministry of Education, Deloitte, etc.)\n-   **Reduced costs by 3x** Increased developers' efficiency and reduced costs by having a user-centered design approach.\n\n[Edtech LMS case study](https://adamfard.com/projects/edtech-saas-design)\n\n![](data:image/png;base64,)\n\n![Kinteract](/static/11ee4946ec945d448974f68da04b0580/d3a75/home-projects-kinteract.png)\n\n![](data:image/png;base64,)\n\n![Qolo](/static/ce1a545bd50de3fc6e9dda1e47327bc6/c946f/home-projects-qolo.png)\n\n##### qolo\n\n## Fintech B2B Payment Platform\n\nQolo is a B2B payments hub for the New Economy with a mission to help businesses navigate today’s complex payments and financial transactions landscape. Qolo supports companies wherever speed, security and cost of payment are important including gig worker payouts, distribution payments, multi-currency and cross-border businesses and modern fintech firms.\n\n-   A developed brand aesthetic almost from scratch;\n-   A fully designed coding-ready responsive app;\n-   An idea brought to life through design.\n\n[Fintech B2B case study](https://adamfard.com/projects/fintech-b2b-platform)\n\n![Doris](/static/doris-1ea71d2f422f35977a7b17bd854b145e.png)![Jeremiah](/static/jeremiah-e0f10b20eb1c671e771bff78f648a4e1.png)![Marina](/static/marina-75a2fe471952fcc44a58cb454954d557.png)![Adam](/static/adam-4d83a19b972188c5e9eafc4af59a702d.png)![Naveed](/static/naveed-982a2ff74cd3e54306fd1d1860678735.png)![Stefan](/static/stefan-d698c2e6c5e40fdcaeb1264a7888f6de.png)![Adam F](/static/adamf-a3d73a12cc966e48ad10c060cb9558f7.png)\n\nWe'reWe'rethetheteamteambehindbehindUXUXPilotPilot——thetheAIAIstartupstartupforforproductproductDesign.Design.\n\n## Our Services\n\nChoose the perfect solution to elevate your product with UX & AI Development:\n\n-   Audit\n-   Design & Dev Retainers\n-   Fixed-Price Projects\n-   MVP Sprint & Build\n-   AI Development\n\n### UX & Tech Audit\n\nComprehensive analysis of UX and technical implementation to uncover usability issues and optimize code quality.\n\n[Fill the form](/contact-us)\n\nWhat's included:\n\n-   **UX Review**\n    \n-   **Technical Code Review**\n    \n-   **Performance Analysis**\n    \n-   **Architecture Assessment**\n    \n-   **Actionable Recommendations**\n    \n\nsample of our deliverables\n\n### Design & DevStream\n\n2x Faster\n\nUnlimited design & dev tasks with dedicated designers and developers, ensuring swift delivery and exceptional quality.\n\n[Fill the form](/contact-us)\n\nWhat's included:\n\n-   **Unlimited design and dev tasks**\n    \n-   **Unlimited Revisions**\n    \n-   **2 Days Turnaround Time**\n    \n-   **Daily Communication**\n    \n-   **1 meeting every 2 weeks**\n    \n-   **Project Management**\n    \n\nsample of our deliverables\n\n### Fixed-Price Projects\n\nIdeal for revamping complex products. We address issues, scale efficiently, and ensure seamless transition for current users.\n\n[Fill the form](/contact-us)\n\nWhat's included:\n\n-   **Fixed-Price with Clear Scope**\n    \n-   **Guaranteed On-Time Delivery**\n    \n-   **Expert Team: Tech Lead, Full-stack developers, PhD Researcher, Product Designer**\n    \n-   **Daily Asynchronous Updates**\n    \n-   **Weekly Strategy Meetings**\n    \n\nsample of our deliverables\n\n### MVP Sprint\n\nGo from idea to market-ready product! We'll handle research, design, and development to help you launch faster.\n\n[Fill the form](/contact-us)\n\nWhat's included:\n\n-   **MVP Design Sprint**\n    \n-   **Market & User Research**\n    \n-   **Interactive Prototype**\n    \n-   **High-Fidelity UI Design**\n    \n-   **Development Implementation**\n    \n-   **Ready-to-Launch Product**\n    \n\nsample of our deliverables\n\n### AI Development\n\nBuild powerful AI solutions with LLM fine-tuning and autonomous AI agents! We develop custom AI systems leveraging the latest in large language models, machine learning, and intelligent automation.\n\n[Fill the form](/contact-us)\n\nWhat's included:\n\n-   **Custom LLM Development & Fine-tuning**\n    \n-   **AI Agent Development**\n    \n-   **Prompt Engineering & Optimization**\n    \n-   **AI System Architecture Design**\n    \n-   **Integration with Existing Systems**\n    \n-   **Performance Testing & Optimization**\n    \n\nsample of our deliverables\n\n[](https://adamfard.com)\n\nConnect with us on\n\n-   [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/company/adam-fard/)\n-   [Youtube](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8sQAC8xQv9UiG5HEGckqIA)\n-   [Behance](https://www.behance.net/AdamFardStudio)\n-   [TikTok](https://www.tiktok.com/@adamfard)\n\n©2025 All Rights Reserved.[Privacy Policy](/privacy-policy)\n\n-   **Solutions**\n-   [Fintech Design](/fintech-design)\n-   [AI Design](/ai-design-agency)\n-   [SaaS Design](/saas-design)\n-   [Edtech Design](/edtech-design)\n-   [UX Consulting](/ux-consulting)\n-   [UX Services](/ux-ui-design-services)\n-   [UX Design Subscription](/unlimited-ux-ui-design-subscription)\n\n-   **UX Agency**\n-   [UX Projects](/ux-projects)\n-   [UX Design Process](/ux-design-process)\n-   [About Us](/about-us)\n\n-   **Growth**\n-   [Social Media Marketing](https://fameclub.adamfard.com)\n\n-   **Directory**\n-   [Agencies (US)](/us/agencies/ui-ux)\n-   [Agencies (UK)](/uk/agencies/ui-ux)\n-   [Agenturen (DE)](/de/agenturen/ui-ux)\n\n-   **Links**\n-   [Careers](/careers)\n-   [UX Blog](/blog)\n-   [Downloads](/download-ux-resources)\n-   [AI Color Generator](https://app.adamfard.com/ai-color-generator)\n-   [Startup Ideas Generator](https://app.adamfard.com/startup-ideas-generator)\n-   [AI UI Generator](https://uxpilot.ai/ai-ui-generator)\n-   [AI Wireframe Generator](https://uxpilot.ai/ai-wireframe-generator)\n-   [AI for UX Design](https://uxpilot.ai/)","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"https://adamfard.com/blog/rental-platform-ux (text/html; charset=UTF-8)","time":{"start":1779177887954,"end":1779177889145}},"id":"prt_e3f4410430016G33MTrV8Fopbm","sessionID":"ses_1c0bd0875ffeDBfk5LNf5rH20A","messageID":"msg