{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779177909332,"sessionID":"ses_1c0bd0875ffeDBfk5LNf5rH20A","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"webfetch","callID":"call_02_j7UZsk2yEPVGPSKf3W9L8621","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"format":"markdown","timeout":30,"url":"https://www.rentable.co/"},"output":"                 \n\n Find Apartments for Rent Near You | Rentable       \n\n[](/)\n\n[Careers](https://www.apartmentiq.io/careers/)\n\n[Favorites](/favorites)\n\n[Advertise With Us](https://advertise.rentable.co)\n\n[Log In](/users/sign_in)\n\n# Every Apartment Near You, In One Place\n\n## Browse 10,377,478 apartments and find the perfect place for you.\n\n \n\nSearch\n\nPlease enter a city.\n\n### Apartments for Rent in Popular Cities\n\n[New York, NY](new-york-ny)\n\n[Los Angeles, CA](los-angeles-ca)\n\n[San Francisco, CA](san-francisco-ca)\n\n[Houston, TX](houston-tx)\n\n[Phoenix, AZ](phoenix-az)\n\n[San Antonio, TX](san-antonio-tx)\n\n[San Diego, CA](san-diego-ca)\n\n[Austin, TX](austin-tx)\n\n[Dallas, TX](dallas-tx)\n\n[Charlotte, NC](charlotte-nc)\n\n[Indianapolis, IN](indianapolis-in)\n\n[View All Cities & Towns](/us)\n\n### Apartments for Rent Across the U.S.\n\n[Madison, WI](madison-wi)\n\n[Memphis, TN](memphis-tn)\n\n[Milwaukee, WI](milwaukee-wi)\n\n[Chicago, IL](chicago-il)\n\n[Minneapolis, MN](minneapolis-mn)\n\n[Columbus, OH](columbus-oh)\n\n[Pittsburgh, PA](pittsburgh-pa)\n\n[Denver, CO](denver-co)\n\n[Champaign, IL](champaign-il)\n\n[St Louis, MO](st-louis-mo)\n\n[Philadelphia, PA](philadelphia-pa)\n\n[Cincinnati, OH](cincinnati-oh)\n\n[Kansas City, MO](kansas-city-mo)\n\n[View All Cities & Towns](/us)\n\n### Apartments for Rent Near College Campuses\n\n[University of Minnesota - Twin Cities](/minneapolis-mn/university-minnesota-twin-cities-apartments/campus)\n\n[Ohio State University](/columbus-oh/ohio-state-university-apartments/campus)\n\n[University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign](/champaign-il/university-of-illinois-at-urbana-champaign-apartments/campus)\n\n[Florida State University](/tallahassee-fl/florida-state-university-apartments/campus)\n\n[University of Florida](/gainesville-fl/university-of-florida-apartments/campus)\n\n[University of Michigan](/ann-arbor-mi/university-of-michigan-ann-arbor-apartments/campus)\n\n[Purdue University-Main Campus](/west-lafayette-in/purdue-university-main-campus-apartments/campus)\n\n[University of Oregon](/eugene-or/university-of-oregon-apartments/campus)\n\n[Texas A&M University - College Station](/college-station-tx/texas-a-m-university-college-station-apartments/campus)\n\n[University of Wisconsin - Madison](/madison-wi/university-wisconsin-madison-apartments/campus)\n\n[University of Wisconsin-Milwaukee](/milwaukee-wi/university-wisconsin-milwaukee-apartments/campus)\n\n[Michigan State University](/east-lansing-mi/michigan-state-university-apartments/campus)\n\n[View All Colleges](/off-campus-housing)\n\n[\n\n...Students can also easily search for off campus housing.\n\n*Curbed*\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n](https://www.curbed.com/2017/6/22/15854516/best-rental-apps-sites-services)\n\n[\n\nBustling with 4/4.5 stars, this app offers a streamlined visual to look for suitable rentals...\n\n*NBC Today*\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n](https://community.today.com/parentingteam/post/top-20-apartment-rental-apps-sites-for-apartment-hunters)\n\nTake Your Search on the Go\n\n*\"This app made finding a new apartment actually convenient. The inventory in my city was the best I've come across.\"*  \n\\-B. Wagner\n\n*\"Great app super easy to use and navigate. It makes getting in contact with properties very easy as well!\"*  \n\\-B. Meyer\n\n[\n\n4.7 (770 reviews)\n\n*195k installs*\n\n](/apps)[\n\n3.6 (212 reviews)\n\n*78k installs*\n\n](/apps)\n\n*Data provided from App Store and Google Play*\n\nFind a Pet Friendly Apartment\n\nRenters with pets trust Rentable. If you're moving with a furry friend, Rentable promises to help you find the perfect place. The rental industry's highest quality, human-verified, pet-friendly listings are just one click away.\n\n[Find Pet Friendly Places](/pet-friendly)\n\nHow Much Rent Can I Afford?\n\nAs a leader in the production of cited rent reports, Rentable's listing prices are more accurate and credible than ever before. If you're looking for a budget calculator you can trust, get started with the Rentable rent affordability calculator.\n\n[Try the Rent Calculator](/affordable-housing-calculator)\n\nWhat is Rentable?\n\nRentable helps renters find apartments. As a well-established apartment marketplace — used by more than 7,000,000 renters — Rentable makes it easy for renters to browse, filter and tour apartments that interest them. Since 2012, Rentable has expanded to more than 300 cities and become a truly nationwide apartment rental marketplace.  \n  \n[More about Rentable](/about)\n\nOver 10,377,478 Apartments to Choose from, and Climbing\n\nRentable provides renters the opportunity to filter through more than two million verified listings, updated on a daily basis. Showcasing an intuitive, mobile-friendly, and trustworthy search platform, Rentable makes it easy to find exactly what renters need.\n\nReal Apartments, Verified by Real People\n\nWhy do our renters rely on Rentable as their preferred apartment marketplace? One word — inventory. Rentable's human-verified listings are reviewed daily by our data experts. From pricing to availability, Rentable listings are validated, justified, and fully endorsed by property managers nationwide.\n\nAdvertising a Property?\n\nMulti-property owner or manager? List your entire portfolio and syndicate your property on Rentable's network.\n\n[Advertise With Us](https://advertise.rentable.co)\n\nTrusted By\n\n[\n\nSurvey Says Millennials Want To Live In New York, Research Suggests They...\n\nSamantha Sharf\n\n\n\n](https://www.forbes.com/sites/samanthasharf/2016/06/13/survey-says-millennials-want-to-live-in-new-york-research-suggests-they-should-live-in-philadelphia/)\n\n[\n\nThe top 10 college t